     0={(∨/'://'⍷⍵)∨'@'∊⍵}link:⍵                       ⍝ We need to catch URLs and email addresses
     link,⍨←(0={(∨/'://'⍷⍵)∨'@'∊⍵}link)/'http://'
 ⍝TODO⍝      link←'\_' '\*' '\~\~'⎕R'\\_' '\\*' '\\~\\~'⍠('Greedy' 0)⊣link
     link,⍨←(('@'∊link)∧'mailto:'{⍺≢⎕C(≢⍺)↑⍵}link)/'mailto:'
